# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:13
translate portuguese bais7_c686fa7a:

    # bai "Ugh. High school."
    bai "Ugh. O liceu."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:14
translate portuguese bais7_ef3686d1:

    # pc "That bad?"
    pc "Tão mau assim?"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:16
translate portuguese bais7_4fac01e7:

    # bai "Well, up until senior year it was fine."
    bai "Bem, até ao último ano estava tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:17
translate portuguese bais7_604b0453:

    # bai "I was popular. Kind of a jock actually. On the basketball and the baseball team."
    bai "Eu era popular. Na verdade, era um tipo de desportista. Fazia parte das equipas de basquetebol e de basebol."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:18
translate portuguese bais7_33c5c7e8:

    # bai "Everything changed during summer break when I told my girlfriend that I thought I might be interested in guys."
    bai "Tudo mudou durante as férias de verão, quando disse à minha namorada que achava que talvez me interessasse por rapazes."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:19
translate portuguese bais7_629195ea:

    # bai "She broke up with me. All my friends stopped talking to me, except when they were calling me names."
    bai "Ela acabou comigo. Todos os meus amigos deixaram de falar comigo, exceto quando me chamavam nomes."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:20
translate portuguese bais7_07e8b64e:

    # bai "That last year of high school was awful."
    bai "Aquele último ano do liceu foi horrível."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:21
translate portuguese bais7_a6d1f112:

    # pc "I'm sorry you had to go through all of that. I thought people were over that homophobic bullshit."
    pc "Lamento que tenhas passado por tudo isso. Pensava que as pessoas já tinham superado essa treta homofóbica."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:22
translate portuguese bais7_f4ee3c48:

    # bai "Not in Texas. I'm sure there are assholes everywhere, but it was pretty bad where I lived."
    bai "Não no Texas. Tenho a certeza de que há idiotas em todo o lado, mas era bastante mau onde eu vivia."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:24
translate portuguese bais7_87ae75f0:

    # bai "Anyway, I pretty much stayed by myself that last year. Barely talked to anybody at school. Or at home. It was hard."
    bai "De qualquer forma, passei praticamente sozinho aquele último ano. Mal falava com ninguém na escola. Ou em casa. Foi difícil."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:25
translate portuguese bais7_1de17344:

    # bai "That's why I wanted to move somewhere far away for college. Somewhere that nobody would know me."
    bai "Foi por isso que quis mudar-me para um sítio longe para ir para a faculdade. Um sítio onde ninguém me conhecesse."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:26
translate portuguese bais7_47f7acfb:

    # pc "Well I think the folks here are more accepting."
    pc "Bem, acho que as pessoas aqui são mais tolerantes."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:27
translate portuguese bais7_1cf47993:

    # pc "I definitely am."
    pc "Eu, sem dúvida, sou."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:28
translate portuguese bais7_d9d623a9:

    # pc "I hope you'll feel comfortable enough to be yourself. You don't have to hide who you are."
    pc "Espero que te sintas à vontade para seres tu mesmo. Não precisas de esconder quem és."

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/bais7.rpy:30
translate portuguese bais7_275b8b31:

    # bai "Thanks, man. It feels really good to know that."
    bai "Obrigado, meu. Faz-me muito bem saber isso."

